ll all the way to the corner.  Star the other guy on the path.  You sometimes will aggro the guy on the platform.  Pulls 1 or 2.<br><br>From gate turn left to balcony.  Move onto stairs and aggro the balcony mob.  Pulls one<br><br>Go back and grab the other.  Pulls one<br><br>Go back to the left balcony stairs.. looking into the courtyard there is a mob next to the statue.  Toss a star.. This results in 1-3 mobs.<br><br>Go back and grab whatever remains in the courtyard. NOTE: DO NOT hug this wall.<br><br>Now go back to the left balcony and run up the path of the courtyard and HUG the wall.  You will aggro two from the other side <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br>Go back and head toward stable, but hug the wall around the corner from balcony... Pulls two more.<br><br>Go back and hug far stable wall and get the other two.<br><br>Head into stable and grab the left guy in the back with a star.  Pulls one<br><br>Back and get right with star  <br><br>Back and get the guy up the ramp.<br><br>By this time back spawn will be happening and you return to the beginning.  You will spend alot less time on your back and more fighting.  Not to mention less risk of train wrecks.  <br><br>Slyst Swiftfang   36 monk<br>Dextor Malthorn   51 warrior <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/uchilli1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Chilli1</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(3/27/01 1:57:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>